A%20New%20Zealand%20MP%20Quits%20Over%20Shoplifting%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20refugee%20to%20be%20elected%20to%20New%20Zealand's%20parliament%20resigned%20Tuesday%20over%20alleged%20shoplifting%2C%20which%20she%20said%20was%20related%20to%20personal%20stress%20and%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGolriz%20Ghahraman%2C%20an%20MP%20for%20the%20centre-left%20Green%20Party%20and%20its%20justice%20spokesperson%2C%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20police%20after%20three%20allegations%20of%20theft%20from%20boutique%20clothing%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmaker%2C%20a%20former%20human%20rights%20lawyer%2C%20said%20her%20actions%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20behaviour%20I%20can%20explain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhahraman%20conceded%20she%20had%20fallen%20short%20of%20the%20standards%20expected%20of%20politicians%20and%20needed%20time%20to%20address%20her%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWork-related%20stress%20led%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bact%20in%20ways%20that%20are%20completely%20out%20of%20character.%20I%20am%20not%20trying%20to%20excuse%20my%20actions%2C%20but%20I%20do%20want%20to%20explain%20them%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mental%20health%20professional%20I%20see%20says%20my%20recent%20behaviour%20is%20consistent%20with%20recent%20events%20giving%20rise%20to%20extreme%20stress%20response%2C%20and%20relating%20to%20previously%20unrecognised%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20let%20down%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20and%20I%20am%20very%20sorry.%20It's%20not%20a%20behaviour%20I%20can%20explain%20because%20it's%20not%20rational%20in%20any%20way%2C%20and%20after%20medical%20evaluation%2C%20I%20understand%20I'm%20not%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran-born%20Ghahraman%2C%2042%2C%20moved%20to%20New%20Zealand%20as%20a%20child%20with%20her%20family%20when%20they%20were%20granted%20political%20asylum%20as%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%2