in%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20broadcaster%20after%20the%20second%20T20I%2C%20gave%20insights%20into%20his%20preparation%20and%20approach%20to%20the%20game%2C%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20focussed%20only%20on%20the%20present%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pleasure%20to%20keep%20improving%20my%20performance%20as%20I%20am%20going%20along.%20The%20range%20I%20have%20is%20god's%20gift%20and%20I%20have%20also%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20it.%20I%20have%20developed%20many%20areas%20of%20my%20game%20and%20I%20am%20getting%20the%20runs%20on%20the%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20Dube%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20way%20to%20his%20an%20unbeaten%2063%20off%2032%20balls%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Dube%20smashed%20four%20towering%20sixes%20and%20five%20fours%2C%20as%20India%20chased%20down%20a%20target%20of%20173%20with%20as%20many%20as%2026%20balls%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20grabbing%20the%20headlines%20with%20the%20willow%20was%20the%20returning%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20hammered%20a%2034-ball%2068.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20think%20only%20about%20the%20present%20and%20not%20about%20the%20forthcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Dube%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20I%20have%20thought%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20future.%20But%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20I%20got%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20present.%20I%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20my%20skills%2C%20so%20that's%20more%20important%20to%20me.%20I%20just%20try%20to%20keep%20myself%20grounded%20and%20try%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20I%20have%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20In%20stark%20contrast%20to%20his%20penchant%20to%20toy%20with%20the%20spinners%2C%2030-year-old%20Dube%20has%20often%20looked%20vulnerable%20against%20the%20short%20deliveries%20bowled%20at%20good%20pace.%20He%20admitted%20that%20the%20standard%20of%20fast%20bowlers%20in%20the%20IPL%20is%20much%20better%20than%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20improving%20his%20game%20against%20short%20balls%2C%20Dube%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20worked%20a%20lot%20on%20it.%20When%20I%20was%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20dominate%20all%20the%20bowlers%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20IPL%20and%20Indian%20cricket%20it%20was%20not%20easy%20as%20bowlers%20were%20bowling%20over%20140km%2Fhr.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20worked%20a%20lot%20with%20side%20arms%2C%20but%20it%20is%20more%20about%20the%20mindset%20which%20I%20worked.%26quot%3B%20Dube%20had%20a%20poor%20start%20for%20India's%20white-ball%20team%20against%20Bangladesh%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20methods%20he%20has%20employed%20that's%20resulted%20in%20a%20significant%20improvement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20credit%20goes%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20and%20Mahi%20bhai%20(MS%20Dhoni)%20because%20I%20always%20had%20this%20game%20in%20me.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20brought%20out%20the%20best%20in%20me.%20They%20have%20always%20encouraged%20me%20and%20said%20that%20they%20believe%20in%20me.%20Stephen%20Fleming%20and%20Mike%20Hussey%20have%20shown%20faith%20in%20me.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20about%20his%20mindset%20as%20a%20finisher%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20all-rounder%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20middle-order%20batsman%2C%20my%20role%20is%20to%20take%20on%20spinners%20and%20improve%20the%20strike%20rate.%20But%20when%20it%20is%20like%20getting%2020-25%20runs%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20have%20seen%20Mahi%20bhai%20do%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20am%20working%20in%20that%20direction.%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20myself%20calm%20and%20composed%20and%20just%20focus%20on%20one%20ball%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705383120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc233fmbg_m