%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IndiGo%20Flier%20Who%20Hit%20Pilot%20Made%20%26quot%3BHoneymoon%26quot%3B%20Claim.%20What%20Cops%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20IndiGo%20passenger%20seen%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20slapping%20a%20pilot%20over%20a%2013-hour%20flight%20delay%20has%20claimed%20to%20the%20police%20that%20he%20lost%20his%20cool%20as%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Goa%20for%20his%20honeymoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahil%20Kataria%2C%2028%2C%20was%20arrested%20last%20evening%20and%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20shortly%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20filmed%20on%20the%20IndiGo%20flight%20(6E-2175)%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Goa%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Sahil%20Kataria%20was%20seen%20charging%20at%20Anup%20Kumar%2C%20the%20flight's%20co-captain%2C%20and%20hitting%20him.%20The%20pilot%20was%20making%20an%20announcement%20about%20delays%20because%20of%20dense%20fog.%20The%20passengers%20had%20reportedly%20been%20in%20the%20aircraft%20for%2010%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChalana%20hai%20chala%2C%20nahi%20chalana%20mat%20chala%2C%20khol%20gate%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fly%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20otherwise%20open%20the%20door)%2C%26quot%3B%20Kataria%20shouted%20at%20the%20pilot%20as%20he%20was%20dragged%20away%20by%20another%20passenger.%20He%20was%20later%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20security%20personnel.%20As%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20many%20called%20for%20his%20arrest%20for%20lashing%20out%20at%20the%20pilot%2C%20%26quot%3Bwho%20was%20only%20doing%20his%20duty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchalana-hai-toh-chala-what-angry-flier-told-indigo-pilot-after-attacking-him-4865504%5C%22%3ERead%7C%20Angry%20Flier%20Who%20Hit%20Pilot%20Apologises%20With%20Folded%20Hands.%20This%20Happens%20Next%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKataria%2C%20who%20reportedly%20runs%20a%20toyshop%20in%20Delhi%2C%20claimed%20he%20was%20incensed%20because%20he%20had%20been%20inordinately%20delayed%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Goa%20for%20his%20honeymoon.%20The%20flight%20was%20meant%20to%20take%20off%20at%207.40%20am%20on%20Sunday%20but%20took%20off%20at%206.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20however%2C%20refuted%20the%20claim%20saying%20he%20had%20in%20fact%20been%20married%20for%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20IndiGo%20said%20the%20passenger%20had%20been%20declared%20'unruly'%20and%20the%20airline%20was%20considering%20including%20him%20in%20the%20no-fly%20list.%20The%20airline%20can%20ban%20an%20unruly%20flier%20for%20up%20to%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20is%20being%20referred%20to%20the%20independent%20internal%20committee%20for%20appropriate%20action%20and%20inclusion%20of%20the%20passenger%20on%20the%20'no-fly%20list'%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20regulatory%20guidelines.%20The%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20our%20passengers%20and%20crew%20are%20of%20paramount%20importance%2C%20and%20we%20maintain%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20towards%20any%20such%20unacceptable%20behaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20IndiGo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilot-blamed-us-passengers-what-russian-woman-evgenia-belskaia-said-on-viral-indigo-video-4867063%5C%22%3ERead%7C%20%26quot%3BPilot%20Blamed%20Us%20Passengers%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20Russian%20Woman%20Said%20On%20Viral%20IndiGo%20Video%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20flights%20have%20been%20disrupted%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20because%20of%20fog%20in%20north%20India.%20In%20new%20rules%20to%20tackle%20the%20airport%20chaos%2C%20the%20aviation%20ministry%20has%20asked%20airlines%20to%20cancel%20flights%20delayed%20beyond%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705383060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvpm5b26o_indigo-pilot-assault_625x300_15_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F