Aviation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20a%20domestic%20flight%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20delayed%20by%20more%20than%20six%20hours%2C%20the%20airline%20shall%20provide%20passengers%20with%20an%20option%20of%20either%20an%20alternate%20flight%20within%20six%20hours%20or%20a%20full%20ticket%20refund.%20Hotel%20accommodation%20can%20only%20be%20provided%20if%20the%20delay%20is%20more%20than%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20video%20has%20amassed%20over%20a%20million%20views%20and%20three%20thousand%20likes.%20Internet%20users%20were%20entirely%20in%20support%20of%20the%20airline%20employee.%20They%20agreed%20that%20she%20doesn't%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20offer%20accommodations%20for%20delays%20due%20to%20conditions%20like%20fog.%20Several%20people%20praised%20Nethra's%20composure%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20indeed%20harsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKudos%20to%20Nethra%2C%20for%20handling%20this%20so%20well%20%40IndiGo6E%20%C2%A0It's%20a%20pity%20that%20%40AuthorPrajnaa%20did%20not%20know%20the%20rules%20fully%20-%20in%20case%20of%20bad%20weather%20%26amp%3B%20acts%20of%20God%20the%20airlines%20are%20not%20bound%20to%20provide%20accommodation.%20Let's%20all%20be%20a%20little%20more%20understandable%20with%20airlines%20over%20the%20crisis%20they%20encounter%20in%20the%20face%20of%20such%20fog%20delays%20!%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20rude%20and%20screaming.%20The%206E%20staff%20is%20treating%20you%20with%20courtesy%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20second%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20a%20fan%20of%20%40IndiGo6E%20%2C%20but%20Nethra%20representing%20it%2C%20handled%20this%20well.%20U%20r%20not%20entitled%20to%20accomodation%2C%20when%20the%20flight%20is%20delayed%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indigo%20airline%20person%20is%20not%20at%20all%20rude%20in%20this.%20She%20is%20sharing%20what%20she%20knows.%20The%20law%20on%20compensation%20allows%20claims%20from%20insurance%20on%20this.%20Here%20delay%20is%20by%20weather%20and%20applicable%20to%20all%20airlines.%20Within%20force%20majure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProfessionally%20handled%20by%20this%20%40IndiGo6E%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndiGo%20also%20replied%20to%20the%20post%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMa'am%2C%20we%20truly%20regret%20this%20discomfort%20and%20assure%20you%20that%20it%20is%20never%20our%20intent%20to%20disrupt%20the%20travel%20plans%20of%20our%20flyers.%20However%2C%20our%20flights%20were%20affected%20due%20to%20the%20consequential%20effect%20of%20bad%20weather%20which%20is%20beyond%20our%20control%20too.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705381980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fid461bao_indigo_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-argues-with-indigo-staff-over-delayed-flight-gets-slammed-online-know-why-4871287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Prajnaa%20was%20travelling%20alone%20and%20her%20IndiGo%20flight%20was%20delayed%20by%20over%20eight%20hours%20due%20to%20bad%20weather%20and%20fog.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-argues-with-indigo-staff-over-delayed-flight-gets-slammed-online-know-why-4871287%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-argues-with-indigo-staff-over-delayed-flight-gets-slammed-online-know-why-4871287%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-argues-with-indigo-staff-over-delayed-flight-gets-slammed-online-know-why-4871287%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RM%20and%20V%20graduate%20as%20elite%20military%20trainees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705381883000%2