20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203%2C%202023.%20Nearly%20200%20people%20have%20died%20and%20over%2050%2C000%20displaced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20see%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state-people%20from%20one%20part%20of%20the%20state%20cannot%20travel%20to%20the%20other%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venugopal%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20violence%2C%20Manipur%20is%20sharply%20divided%20between%20the%20hills%20where%20the%20population%20is%20dominated%20by%20Kukis%20and%20the%20plains%20including%20capital%20Imphal%20which%20is%20Meitei%20dominated%2C%20with%20people%20from%20the%20two%20communities%20staying%20in%20their%20areas%20and%20not%20being%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20parts%20where%20the%20other%20community%20is%20dominant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYet%20amid%20all%20this%20division%2C%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20met%20Meitei%20groups%20they%20were%20very%20happy%20to%20see%20him%20yesterday%20and%20when%20he%20met%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20today%2C%20they%20too%20were%20very%20happy%20to%20see%20him.%20The%20communities%20might%20be%20divided%20in%20Manipur%20but%20they%20are%20united%20in%20their%20affection%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDay%20two%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20saw%20Gandhi%20beginning%20his%20journey%20from%20Sekmei%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Imphal%20West%2C%20passing%20through%20Kangpokpi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20that%20that%20saw%20large-scale%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20to%20Senapati%20(which%20has%20a%20predominantly%20Naga%20population)%20before%20stopping%20for%20the%20night%20in%20Khuzama%2C%20Nagaland%20on%20the%20Manipur-Nagaland%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16091824%2FRG-in-Manipur-photo-by-congress-day-2-BJNY.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16091824%2FRG-in-Manipur-photo-by-congress-day-2-BJNY.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16091824%2FRG-in-Manipur-photo-by-congress-day-2-BJNY-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16091824%2FRG-in-Manipur-photo-by-congress-day-2-BJNY-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Manipur%20on%20day%20two%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Make%20PM%20visit%20Manipur%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20told%20reporters%20in%20Karong%20village%2C%20Senapati%2C%20that%20the%20civil%20groups%20that%20had%20met%20Gandhi%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20wanted%20him%20to%20raise%20their%20demand%20in%20parliament%20that%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20visit%20Manipur%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20when%20we%20used%20to%20come%20to%20Manipur%2C%20we%20used%20to%20meet%20Manipuri%20organisations.%20Today%20in%20Manipur%20we%20have%20to%20meet%20organisations%20of%20different%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20has%20told%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20sensitive%2C%20transparent%2C%20accountable%2