rcussions.%20In%20contrast%2C%20social%20media%20accounts%20could%20be%20banned%20on%20Facebook%20and%20X%2C%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20web%20of%20misinformation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20depicting%20a%20decapitated%20body%20is%20circulating%20with%20a%20caption%20in%20Hindi%2C%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20Hamas%20which%20is%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20regional%20parties.%20So%2C%20think%20about%20what%20you%20have%20to%20do.%20Consider%20the%20fate%20of%20your%20country%2C%20your%20children%2C%20your%20tomorrow.%20You%20yourself%20are%20wise.%20Look%20at%20the%20actions%20of%20Hamas%20scoundrels%20with%20open%20eyes%20and%20consider%20those%20who%20support%20them.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20those%20backing%20these%20individuals%20today%20are%20the%20same%20individuals%20working%20to%20convert%20India%20into%20an%20Islamic%20country.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20seeing%20an%20Islamic%20State%20or%20Ghazwatul%20Hind%20in%20India%2C%20I%20urge%20all%20of%20you%20to%20recognise%20that%20the%20viral%20video%20alone%20won%E2%80%99t%20bring%20about%20change.%20Every%20Hindu%20must%20strive%20to%20prevent%20the%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20opposition%20party%20from%20forming%20the%20government%20in%20India%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20painful%20future%20for%20all%20of%20us%20and%20our%20families.%20Every%20Hindu%20should%20make%20every%20effort%20to%20support%20Modi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Hind%2C%20Jai%20Bharat%2C%20Vande%20Mataram.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20attack%20is%20being%20exploited%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20to%20instil%20fear%20among%20Indians%2C%20particularly%20Hindus%2C%20by%20suggesting%20that%20something%20even%20more%20ominous%20than%20the%20events%20in%20Israel%20will%20soon%20transpire%20in%20India.%20These%20messages%2C%20which%20have%20gone