20they%20have%20developed%20technology%20that%20can%20imitate%20someone's%20handwriting%20based%20on%20just%20a%20few%20paragraphs%20of%20written%20material.%20To%20accomplish%20that%2C%20the%20researchers%20used%20a%20transformer%20model%2C%20a%20type%20of%20neural%20network%20designed%20to%20learn%20context%20and%20meaning%20in%20sequential%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20at%20MBZUAI%2C%20which%20calls%20itself%20the%20world's%20first%20AI%20university%2C%20has%20been%20granted%20a%20patent%20by%20the%20US%20Patent%20and%20Trademark%20Office%20for%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20have%20not%20yet%20released%20the%20feature%2C%20but%20it%20represents%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20an%20area%20that%20has%20drawn%20interest%20from%20academics%20for%20years.%20There%20have%20been%20apps%20and%20even%20robots%20that%20can%20generate%20handwriting%2C%20but%20recent%20advances%20in%20AI%20have%20accelerated%20character%20recognition%20techniques%20dramatically.%20As%20with%20other%20AI%20tools%2C%20however%2C%20it's%20unclear%20if%20the%20benefits%20will%20outweigh%20the%20harms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20could%20help%20the%20injured%20to%20write%20without%20picking%20up%20a%20pen%2C%20but%20it%20also%20risks%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20mass%20forgeries%20and%20misuse.%20%C2%A0The%20tool%20will%20need%20to%20be%20deployed%20thoughtfully%2C%20two%20of%20the%20researchers%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20have%20to%20create%20public%20awareness%20and%20develop%20tools%20to%20combat%20forgery%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hisham%20Cholakkal%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20for%20computer%20vision%20at%20MBZUAI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20developing%20an%20anti-virus%20for%20a%20virus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20concerns%2C%20the%20inventors%20said%20they%20plan%20to%20apply%20their%20research%20to%20real-world%20applications%20within%20months%20-%20and%20they're%20looking%20for%20commercial%20collaborators.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20decoding%20doctors'%20handwriting%20to%20crafting%20personalized%20advertising%2C%20the%20potential%20of%20this%20development%20is%20huge%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rao%20Muhammad%20Anwer%2C%20also%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20computer%20vision%20at%20MBZUAI.%20%C2%A0The%20technology%20could%20also%20be%20used%20to%20generate%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20synthetic%20data%20to%20improve%20how%20other%20AI%20models%20process%20handwriting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20still%20more%20to%20work%20to%20do%2C%20however.%20The%20researchers'%20transformer%20model%2C%20trained%20from%20publicly%20available%20handwritten%20texts%2C%20can%20learn%20and%20write%20in%20English%20and%2C%20with%20some%20success%2C%20in%20French.%20But%20the%20team%20said%20they%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20crack%20handwritten%20text%20in%20Arabic.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705367580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj4lbd4g_artificial-intelligence_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fartificial-intelligence-can-convincingly-mimic-a-persons-handwriting-study-4870706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20already%20allow%20people%20to%20generate%20eerily%20convincing%20voice%20clones%20and%20deepfake%20videos.%20Soon%2C%20AI%20could%20also%20be%20used%20to%20mimic%20a%20person's%20handwriting%20style.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fartificial-intelligence-can-convincingly-mimic-a-persons-handwriting-study-4870706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fartificial