%2086-year-old%20father%2C%20King%20Harald%20V%2C%20who%20now%20rarely%20appears%20in%20public%20because%20of%20his%20ill%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoyal%20%E2%80%98soap%20opera%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20kings%20and%20queens%20have%20generally%20ceremonial%20roles%2C%20with%20scant%20political%20power.%20This%20applies%20to%20the%20princely%20houses%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fluxembourg%2Ft-40075872%5C%22%3ELuxembourg%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Liechtenstein%2C%20along%20with%20the%20dwarf%20state%20of%20Monaco%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Falbert-ii%2Ft-38292497%5C%22%3EPrince%20Albert%20II%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20relatively%20strong%20position.%20Another%20dwarf%20state%2C%20Andorra%2C%20tucked%20between%20the%20high%20valley%20of%20France%20and%20Spain%2C%20always%20has%20two%20co-princes%20who%20act%20as%20heads%20of%20state.%20One%20prince%20is%20the%20Spanish%20bishop%20of%20Urgell%3B%20the%20other%20is%20the%20president%20of%20France.%20This%20means%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Femmanuel-macron%2Ft-38774225%5C%22%3EEmmanuel%20Macron%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20only%20currently%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20France%2C%20but%20also%20a%20prince%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20democracy%20of%20Andorra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20elective%20monarchy%20in%20Europe%20where%20the%20throne%20is%20not%20hereditary%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fvatican%2Ft-39325063%5C%22%3E%20the%20Vatican%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpope-francis%2Ft-17449437%5C%22%3EPope%20Francis%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20only%20heads%20the%20Catholic%20Church%2C%20but%20is%20also%20the%20absolute%20ruler%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20smallest%20state%3A%20Vatican%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20most%20citizens%20of%20states%20with%20a%20monarchical%20order%20actually%20enjoy%20their%20monarchy%2C%E2%80%9D%20University%20of%20Potsdam%20historian%20and%20royals%20expert%20Monika%20Wienfort%20said.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20serious%20efforts%20to%20abolish%20this%20form%20of%20government%20in%20the%20seven%20sovereign%20royal%20houses%20and%20five%20principalities%20in%20Europe.%20Resignations%20and%20successions%20have%20been%20seamless%20apart%20from%20minor%20protests%20by%20republican-minded%20groups%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyalty%20has%20persisted%20throughout%20Europe%20wherever%20there%20were%20no%20revolutionary%20upheavals%2C%20such%20as%20those%20in%20France%2C%20Italy%2C%20Austria%20or%20Germany.%20As%20almost%20all%20royal%20houses%20are%20somehow%20related%20to%20each%20other%2C%20and%20chiefly%20to%20German%20nobility%2C%20there%20would%20always%20be%20the%20possibility%20of%20moving%20in%20with%20relatives%20in%20a%20pinch%2C%20Wienfort%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20houses%20thrive%20on%20tradition%2C%20gossip%2C%20scandals%20and%20the%20public%20display%20of%20a%20happy%20family%20life%2C%20increasingly%20free%20of%20pomp%20and%20glitter.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20we%E2%80%99re%20a%20soap%20opera%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20United%20Kingdom%E2%80%99s%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fking-charles-iii%2Ft-36992023%5C%22%3EPrince%20Charles%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20about%20his%20family%20in%202008.%20His%20father%2C%20Philip%2C%20once%20also%20described%20the%20Windsors%20as%20a%20company%20tasked%20with%20producing%20beautiful%20images%20to%20aspire%20to%20in%20return%20for%20taxpayers%E2%80%99%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E43%20monarchies%20globally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monarchy%20model%20rules%20in%2022%25%20of%20the%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20or%2043%20of%20the%20194%20formally%20recognized%20states.%20In%20addition%20to%20Europe%2C%20monarchies%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Africa%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Asia.%20Many%20date%20back%20to%20the%20British%20Empire%2C%20and%20the%20British%20king%20is%20still%20the%20head%20of%20state%20in%2014%20countries%20outside%20Europe%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Canada%20and%20Australia.%20Japan%20is%20the%20only%20empire%20in%20the%20world%2C%20though%20the%20Tenno%20has%20purely%20ceremonial%20duties%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20six%20countries%2C%20the%20monarch%2C%20sheikh%20or%20emir%20is%20the%20absolute%20ruler%20without%20parliamentary%20or%20judicial%20control%3A%20Brunei%2C%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Eswatini%20(formerly%20Swaziland)%20and%20the%20aforementioned%20Vatican%20City.%20In%20some%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20Jordan%20or%20Morocco%2C%20the%20king%20has%20political%20power%20determined%20by%20the%20constitution.%20In%20Asia%2C%20Malaysia%20has%20the%20only%20major%20elective%20monarchy%2C%20currently%20held%20by%20Sultan%20Abdullah%20Sultan%20Ahmad%20Shah%2C%20determined%20by%20the%20sultans%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20nine%20provinces.%20In%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20the%20office%20of%20head%20of%20state%20also%20rotates%20among%20the%20emirs%2C%20the%20authoritarian%20leaders%20of%20their%20respective%20principalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20tabloid%20press%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20publicly%20report%20royal%20dramas%2C%20but%20gossip%20about%20monarchs%20is%20big%20business%20in%20Europe.%20The%20market%20leader%20is%20still%20the%20British%20royal%20family%2C%20even%20without%20the%20queen%2C%20who%20reigned%20for%2070%20years%20and%20died%20in%202022.%20Public%20interest%20in%20the%20dysfunctional%20family%20dramas%20surrounding%20King%20Charles%3B%20his%20sons%2C%20William%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fharry%2Ft-38325177%5C%22%3EHarry%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20wife%2C%20Camilla%2C%20remains%20steady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fascination%20stems%20from%20the%20spectacular%20in%20the%20everyday%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wienfort%20said.%20The%20royals%20do%20completely%20normal%20things%20such%20as%20marry%2C%20raise%20children%20and%20die.%20But%20their%20biographies%20are%20representative%20and%20luxurious%2C%20or%20even%20pompous%2C%20she%20said.%20People%20want%20to%20look%20at%20carriages%2C%20uniforms%2C%20dresses%20and%20castles%2C%20even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20particular%20awe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20monarch%20is%20also%20fairy%20tale-level%20lucrative.%20The%20richest%20king%20in%20the%20world%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fthailand%2Ft-63342744%5C%22%3EThailand%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20Rama%20X%2C%20is%20worth%20%2430%20billion%20to%20%2443%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC27.3-%E2%82%AC39%20billion)%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20by%20US%20business%20magazines.%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20richest%20prince%20is%20Hans-Adam%20II%20of%20Liechtenstein%2C%20with%20about%20%243.5%20billion.%20UK%20King%20Charles%20III%20has%20a%20private%20fortune%20of%20%241.8%20billion%20(%E2%82%AC1.6%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Margarethe%20II%20of%20Denmark%20will%20hand%20over%20a%20comparatively%20meagre%20%2430%20million%20in%20the%20crown%E2%80%99s%20coffers%20to%20her%20son%20Frederik%2C%20though%20it%20would%20certainly%20be%20enough%20to%20hold%20a%20veritable%20court.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20still%20significantly%20more%20than%20what%20the%20Spanish%20king%20has%20to%20make%20do%20with%20%E2%80%94%20just%20%2410%20million%2C%20putting%20him%20in%20last%20place%20among%20royals%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsomething-common-in-the-state-of-denmark-a-world-of-royals%2Fa-67972921%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705324213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15175806%2Fimage-1746.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Facross-the-world-monarchs-continue-to-reign%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Denmark%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20king.%20Despite%20transitions%20toward%20democracy%2C%20royalty%20abounds%20worldwide%2C%20and%20some%20monarchs%20enjoy%20absolute%20rule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Facross-the-world-monarchs-continue-to-reign%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20World%20May%20Have%20Its%20First%20Trillionaire%20in%2010%20Years%2C%20but%20Eradicating%20Poverty%20Will%20Take%20230%3A%20Oxfam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15173435%2FMumbai.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%202020s%20are%20a%20decade%20of%20crisis%2C%20the%20relief%20NGO%20Oxfam%20said%20in%20its%20latest%20report%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20world%20today%20faces%20a%20fundamental%20choice%20between%20ushering%20in%20an%20age%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbillionaire%20supremacy%E2%80%9D%20and%20repurposing%20the%20economy%20to%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20statistic%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foxfamilibrary.openrepository.com%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F10546%2F621583%2Fbp-inequality-inc-150124-en.pdf%5C%22%3Ethis%20report%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Inequality%20Inc.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20that%20since%202020%2C%20five%20billion%20people%20%E2%80%93%2060%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20%E2%80%93%20grew%20poorer%20but%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20five%20richest%20men%20doubled%20their%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxfam%20also%20estimated%20that%20if%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20five%20richest%20billionaires%20continued%20to%20rise%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20as%20it%20has%20over%20the%20past%20half-decade%2C%20the%20world%20will%20see%20its%20first%20trillionaire%20within%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20will%20not%20eliminate%20poverty%20for%20230%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20three%20years%2C%20the%20world%20has%20seen%20a%20global%20pandemic%2C%20war%20and%20a%20cost-of-living%20crisis%2C%20Oxfam%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20did%20not%20just%20widen%20the%20gulf%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cbetween%20an%20oligarchic%20few%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20said%20that%20increasing%20monopolisation%20had%20%E2%80%9Csupercharged%E2%80%9D%20global%20corporate%20power%2C%20which%20it%20described%20as%20pursuing%20higher%20returns%20to%20shareholders%20above%20all%20other%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20on%20to%20identify%20four%20ways%20in%20which%20corporate%20power%20fuelled%20inequality%3A%20forcing%20wages%20down%20and%20directing%20profits%20to%20the%20super-rich%3B%20avoiding%20taxes%3B%20privatising%20public%20services%3B%20and%20driving%20(and%20spinning%20the%20truth%20about)%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxfam%20highlighted%20how%20the%20latter%20two%20ways%20could%20drive%20inequalities%20along%20gender%2C%20race%2C%20caste%20or%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz0deAkw42DM%3Fsi%3DBxSK9qtgPSUwFZu3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20privatisation%20in%20India%2C%20it%20said%20that%20Dalits%20faced%20higher%20costs%20and%20overt%20discrimination%20in%20the%20private%20healthcare%20and%20education%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxfam%20also%20said%20that%20while%20the%20World%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20private%20sector%20arm%20had%20invested%20over%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20private%20health%20sector%2C%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20published%20a%20single%20evaluation%20of%20its%20health%20projects%20in%20India%20since%20these%20started%20over%2025%20years%20ago.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSupporting%20private%20healthcare%20in%20a%20context%20where%2037%25%20of%20Indians%20experience%20catastrophic%20health%20expenditures%20in%20private%20hospitals%20appears%20to%20run%20counter%20to%20the%20World%20Bank%20Group%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20poverty%20reduction%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20had%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfam.org%2Fen%2Fresearch%2Ffirst-do-no-harm-examining-impact-ifcs-support-private-healthcare-india%5C%22%3Eearlier%20study%20published%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20this%20arm%20of%20the%20World%20Bank%20had%20invested%20in%20high-end%20urban%20hospitals%20in%20India%2C%20adding%20that%20several%20such%20hospitals%20had%20consistently%20failed%20to%20provide%20free%20care%20to%20the%20poor%20despite%20being%20required%20to%20do%20so%20in%20return%20for%20receiving%20subsidised%20government%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Ffour-things-india-must-do-to-achieve-economic-equality-social-justice%5C%22%3EFour%20Things%20India%20Must%20Do%20to%20Achieve%20Economic%20Equality%2C%20Social%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENear%20the%20end%20of%20its%20report%2C%20Oxfam%20called%20on%20governments%20to%20reduce%20wealth%20inequality%20by%20creating%20a%20dynamic%20and%20effective%20state%2C%20reining%20in%20corporate%20power%20and%20freeing%20businesses%20from%20%E2%80%9Cshareholder%20greed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20radical.%20What%E2%80%99s%20radical%20is%20letting%20such%20extremes%20persist%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRebecca_Riddell%2Fstatus%2F1746685875910508812%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20Rebecca%20Riddell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20authors%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmitabh%20Behar%2C%20Oxfam%20International%E2%80%99s%20interim%20executive%20director%2C%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20rein%20in%20%E2%80%9Crunaway%20corporate%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20evidence.%20We%20know%20the%20history.%20Public%20power%20can%20rein%20in%20runaway%20corporate%20power%20and%20inequality%20%E2%80%93%20shaping%20the%20market%20to%20be%20fairer%20and%20free%20from%20billionaire%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfam.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2Fwealth-five-richest-men-doubles-2020-five-billion-people-made-poorer-decade-division%5C%22%3EOxfam%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CGovernments%20must%20intervene%20to%20break%20up%20monopolies%2C%20empower%20workers%2C%20tax%20these%20massive%20corporate%20profits%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20invest%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20public%20goods%20and%20services.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705323631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15173435%2FMumbai.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmay-have-first-trillionaire-in-ten-years-oxfam%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opening%20statistic%20of%20Oxfam's%20latest%20report%20is%20that%20since%202020%2C%20five%20billion%20people%20%E2%80%93%2060%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20%E2%80%93%20grew%20poorer%20but%20the%20world's%20five%20richest%20men%20doubled%20their%20wealth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmay-have-first-trillionaire-in-ten-years-oxfam%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fitch%20assigns%20'BB(EXP)'%20rating%20to%20Shriram%20Finance's%20proposed%20US%20bonds%20issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705323453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-11%2F10%2Ffull%2F1668094872-8095.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffitch-assigns-bb-exp-rating-to-shriram-finance-s-proposed-us-bonds-issue-124011500628_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'BB(EXP)'%20rating%20reflects%20that%20an%20issuer%20has%20some%20risk%20of%20default%20but%20is%20still%20a%20safer%20investment%20compared%20to%20others%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffitch-assigns-bb-exp-rating-to-shriram-finance-s-proposed-us-bonds-issue-124011500628_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffitch-assigns-bb-exp-rating-to-shriram-finance-s-proposed-us-bonds-issue-124011500628_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ffitch-assigns-bb-exp-rating-to-shriram-finance-s-proposed-us-bonds-issue-124011500628_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'It's%20Divided%2C%20Not%20United%20India'%3A%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20on%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15174928%2FEffect-67.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20detailed%2040-minute%20interview%2C%20where%20he%20explains%20at%20length%20how%20he%20views%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20(consecration)%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20murti%20at%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%2022%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20has%20said%20that%20he%20has%20not%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony.%20He%20added%20that%20if%20he%20were%20to%20be%20invited%20he%20would%20certainly%20go%20to%20Ayodhya%20but%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20(consecration)%20ceremony.%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20said%20he%20does%20not%20know%20if%20the%20other%20Shankaracharyas%20(of%20Puri%2C%20Dwarka%2C%20Sringeri)%20have%20been%20invited%20but%20equally%20clearly%20said%20that%20none%20of%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20will%20be%20attending%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20special%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20recorded%20face-to-face%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%C2%A0%2015%2C%20a%20week%20before%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20explained%20in%20detail%20why%20he%20will%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqkSAOYTSgYo%3Fsi%3D9bHXUY3iUps6jOHJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20leave%20you%20to%20get%20the%20details%20from%20the%20interview%2C%20where%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20in%20Hindi%20and%20the%20questions%20are%20a%20mixture%20of%20English%20and%20Hindi.%20However%2C%20let%20me%20in%20broad%20terms%20point%20out%20that%20Swami%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20argument%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20against%20the%20dharma%20shastras%20to%20perform%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20of%20a%20murti%20before%20the%20temple%20is%20complete.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20mahurat%20has%20not%20been%20correctly%20chosen%20revealing%20that%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20Jyotish%20in%20Kashi%20was%20told%20to%20identify%20a%20mahurat%20in%20January%20rather%20than%20the%20most%20appropriate%20mahurat%20for%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20is%20not%20anti-Modi%20but%20accepted%20that%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20as%20well%20as%20the%20propaganda%20surrounding%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20have%20politicised%20the%20temple.%20He%20said%20he%20completely%20agreed%20with%20comments%20made%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20and%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20January%2014%20where%20the%20Shankaracharya%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20they%20have%20responsibility%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20There%20are%20rules%20and%20restrictions%20in%20the%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20domain%20and%20these%20rules%20should%20be%20followed.%20Interfering%20in%20every%20area%20by%20politicians%20is%20insanity%E2%80%A6overstepping%20these%20rules%20for%20propagating%20one%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20an%20act%20of%20rebellion%20against%20God.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20was%20hinting%20at%20Modi%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Jyotish%20Peeth%20said%20nothing%20has%20been%20hidden%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20clear%20that%20the%20reference%20is%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20was%20asked%20how%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20who%20Hindus%20view%20as%20Maryada%20Purushottam%2C%20would%20view%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20his%20name%20at%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%20The%20Swami%20agreed%20that%20he%20is%20worried%20that%20the%20politicization%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20is%20dividing%20India%20rather%20than%20uniting%20India%20and%20also%20creating%20divisions%20among%20its%20Hindu%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20was%20asked%20whether%20he%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20temples%20replacing%20existing%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20and%20said%20that%20that%20the%20issue%20should%20be%20resolved%20by%20consensus%20with%20wise%20Hindus%20and%20wise%20Muslims%20sitting%20together%20and%20people%20returning%20to%20each%20other%20what%20has%20been%20wrongly%20taken%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20was%20asked%20questions%20about%20himself.%20He%20responded%20to%20claims%20that%20he%20is%20the%20one%20who%20is%20politicizing%20the%20temple%20as%20well%20as%20online%20fake%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20visited%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%20to%20spread%20a%20chadhar.%20He%20also%20responded%20to%20the%20accusation%20that%20he%20is%20behaving%20and%20speaking%20like%20a%20Congressman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20being%20very%20careful%20in%20paraphrasing%20the%20broad%20points%20made%20by%20the%20Shankaracharya%20because%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20misinterpret%20him%20or%20convey%20a%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20views.%20Inevitably%20that%20will%20mislead%20but%20also%20add%20to%20the%20confusion%20and%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20best%20that%20you%20should%20see%20this%20interview%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20lengthy%2040-minute%20interview%20and%20I%20believe%20the%20first%20by%20any%20of%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20where%20he%20explains%20at%20such%20length%20his%20views%20on%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20politicisation%20that%20is%20happening%20as%20well%20as%20other%20associated%20matters%20such%20as%20whether%20temples%20should%20replace%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20and%20how%20he%20responds%20to%20criticism%20of%20himself%2C%20both%20online%20and%20made%20by%20BJP%20supporters%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20what%20I%20will%20do%20is%20to%20give%20you%20the%20list%20of%20questions%20so%20you%20can%20both%20see%20the%20range%20of%20issues%20covered%20and%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20interview%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Why%20have%20you%20refused%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20next%20Monday%2C%20January%2022%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20In%20a%20video%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20you%20have%20said%20I%20am%20not%20anti-Modi%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20anti-dharma%20shastra%20either.%20Can%20you%20explain%20why%20it%20will%20be%20against%20the%20shastras%20if%20you%20attend%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20The%20temple%20is%20not%20complete%20and%20will%20not%20be%20for%20perhaps%20two%20more%20years.%20Even%20its%20%3Cem%3Eshikar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spire)%20has%20not%20been%20built.%20Do%20the%20shastras%20permit%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20to%20take%20place%20in%20an%20unfinished%20and%20incomplete%20temple%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20What%20about%20garbhagriha%2Fmahurat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20What%20about%20the%20other%20three%20Shankaracharyas%20from%20Puri%2C%20Dwarka%20and%20Sringeri%3F%20Will%20they%20be%20attending%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%3F%20Or%20have%20all%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20refused%20the%20invitation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20central%20person%20at%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20will%20be%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20Speaking%20about%20this%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20has%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20scriptures%20have%20clearly%20mentioned%20who%20can%20touch%20the%20idol.%20What%20will%20I%20do%20there%20during%20the%20consecration%3F%20Modi%20ji%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20touch%20the%20idol.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20stand%20there%20and%20clap%20to%20applaud%20him.%20I%20know%20the%20dignity%20of%20my%20position.%20This%20isn%E2%80%99t%20ego.%E2%80%9D%20Do%20you%20share%20that%20view%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6)%C2%A0%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20has%20become%20a%20rajnitik%20event%20rather%20than%20a%20dharmik%20event.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7)%C2%A0%20On%20Saturday%20in%20Bengal%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20have%20their%20limits%20and%20they%20have%20responsibility%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20There%20are%20rules%20and%20restrictions%20in%20the%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20domain%20and%20these%20rules%20should%20be%20followed.%20Interfering%20in%20every%20area%20by%20politicians%20is%20insanity%E2%80%A6overstepping%20these%20rules%20for%20propagating%20one%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20an%20act%20of%20rebellion%20against%20God.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Do%20you%20agree%3F%20(Hindu%2014%2F1)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8)%20Are%20you%20worried%20that%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20been%20politicised%20and%20this%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20and%20all%20the%20politics%20and%20propaganda%20around%20it%20could%20divide%20India%20rather%20than%20unite%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9)%20Hindus%20view%20Lord%20Ram%20as%20Maryada%20Purushottam.%20How%20would%20he%20view%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20his%20name%20at%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10)%20The%20Ayodhya%20temple%20is%20being%20built.%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20see%20similar%20temples%20in%20place%20of%20mosques%20in%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11)%20The%20BJP%20says%20that%20in%20refusing%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtha%20you%20are%20the%20one%20who%20is%20introducing%20politics.%20There%20are%20also%20fake%20claims%20about%20you%20online.%20One%20such%20is%20that%20you%20have%20visited%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%20to%20spread%20a%20chadhar.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20this%20treatment%20of%20yourself%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20You%E2%80%99re%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20Congressman%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12)%C2%A0%20Your%20pain%20and%20unhappiness%20have%20been%20clear%20and%20visible%20in%20this%20interview.%20Am%20I%20right%20in%20saying%20at%20a%20moment%20which%20should%20be%20one%20of%20happiness%20you%20are%20in%20fact%20sad%20and%20pained%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705321418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15174928%2FEffect-67.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-its-divided-not-united-india-shankaracharya-of-jyotish-peeth-on-ayodhya-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%20Saraswati%20tells%20Karan%20Thapar%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20he%20wasn't%20invited%20for%20the%20consecration%2C%20but%20even%20if%20he%20had%20been%20invited%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20attended%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-its-divided-not-united-india-shankaracharya-of-jyotish-peeth-on-ayodhya-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inquest%20to%20reveal%20fate%20of%20British%20men%20who%20died%20in%20Ukraine%20-%20as%20family%20say%20they%20were%20'executed'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705321380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F22%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-chris-parry-east-ukraine_5970962.jpg%3F20221119100540%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Finquest-to-reveal-fate-of-british-men-who-died-in-ukraine-as-family-say-they-were-executed-13048924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20inquest%20will%20reveal%20what%20happened%20to%20two%20British%20aid%20workers%20who%20died%20in%20Ukraine%20-%20as%20the%20family%20of%20one%20say%20they%20were%20executed%2C%20possibly%20by%20Wagner%20Group%20mercenaries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Finquest-to-reveal-fate-of-british-men-who-died-in-ukraine-as-family-say-they-were-executed-13048924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fa