0Surprisingly%2C%20they%20declined%2C%20suggesting%20I%20either%20give%20them%20to%20a%20scrap%20collector%20or%20to%20my%20local%20newspaper%20vendor%2C%20who%20could%20sell%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjayan%20did%20not%20want%20to%20sell%20the%20items%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrap%20collector%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20decided%20to%20think%20of%20some%20other%20way.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20establish%20a%20website%20for%20people%20to%20donate%20and%20acquire%20items%20based%20on%20their%20needs%2C%20funding%20became%20a%20hurdle.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20company%20where%20I%20work%20generously%20provided%20me%20with%20a%20storage%20space.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20without%20a%20fixed%20website%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ajayan%20Namminipurthu%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sanathya%20Foundation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-1704891553-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22w