20her%20physical%20disability%20certificate.%20Here%2C%20she%20met%20a%20lady%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20both%20feet%20and%20had%20travelled%20to%20Bengaluru%20from%20Tumakuru%2C%20with%20an%20infant%20in%20tow.%20Veena%20watched%20in%20awe%20as%20that%20lady%20fed%20her%20baby%20and%20played%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etroubles%20felt%20inconsequential%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20front%20of%20hers.%20She%20was%20happy%20and%20even%20managed%20to%20cook.%20She%20got%20her%20baby%20from%20so%20far%20away%20and%20led%20a%20regular%20life.%20So%20I%20thought%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20I%3F%20I%20too%20could%20and%20would%20do%20everything%20I%20ever%20wanted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%20in%20January%202013%2C%20with%20hardly%20two%20months%20for%20the%20board%20exams%2C%20Veena%20started%20going%20for%20tuition%20classes%2C%20assisted%20by%20her%20father.%20She%20managed%20to%20pass%20the%20exams%20with%20a%20decent%20score.%20Since%20going%20to%20college%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Bengaluru%20would%20be%20difficult%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20Puducherry%20to%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20place%20and%20pursued%20her%20degrees%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20post-graduation%2C%20she%20switched%20jobs%20from%20banks%20to%20IT%20but%20the%20stress%20of%20a%20desk%20job%20was%20too%20much%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20project%20with%20a%20South%20American%20company%2C%20which%20meant%20office%20work%20from%209%20to%206%20followed%20by%20meetings%20at%209%3A30%20pm%20which%20often%20got%20over%20by%201%20to%202%20am.%20The%20stress%20on%20my%20leg%20led%20to%20infection%20and%20hospitalisation%20for%2015%20days.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20t